HEADWORD: Gila monster
<hw>Gi"la mon"ster</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A large
tuberculated lizard (<spn>Heloderma suspectum</spn>) native of the dry
plains of Arizona, New Mexico, etc. It is the only lizard known to have
venomous teeth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gilbert</ent>⟦br⟧
